or-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b3247e7dbc632a4b9e79d7e45fbef703" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Jocelyne-De-Nicola-130x200.jpg" width="65" height="100" alt="Jocelyne De Nicola" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Jocelyne De Nicola"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/jocelyne-de-nicola/">View all articles by Jocelyne De Nicola</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/05/opera-di-roma-rienzi/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Opera di Roma: &#8220;Rienzi&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/05/firenze-teatro-del-maggio-musicale-fiorentino-don-carlo/" rel="next">Firenze, Teatro del Maggio Musicale Fiorentino: “Don Carlo” <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/05/marsiglia-opera-municipal-la-clemenza-di-tito/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='52808' id='comment_post_ID' /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_parent' id='comment_parent' value='0' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="f6f759556e" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="100"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/' title='Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/opera-di-firenze-cortile-di-palazzo-pitti-la-traviata/' title='Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="La traviata (prima) Simone Donati - TerraProject - Contrasto (10)" title="Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-puritani-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/' title='“I Puritani” al Teatro Real di Madrid'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/u